- None

## Context
Fixed PR #46 blockers: one CI failure (test-harness) and one CodeRabbit review comment. The CI failure was caused by a test still enforcing the old directory-only pattern validation that this PR intentionally removed. The deeper issue was that domain_resolve_path and query_by_path lacked exact filepath matching, making file-level patterns accepted but unresolvable. Added exact-match UNION clauses to both functions, trimmed whitespace in validate_pattern per review feedback, and updated the test to verify the new behavior. All tests pass locally.

